sys_script_include.description:
Use to convert a glidelist to records, each item in the list is saved to the target table as a record, primarly used for reporting purposes. Call this in a BR like:
new GlideListToRecords().execute( current.getValue('u_managers'), current.getValue('sys_id'), 'u_group_managers' 'u_group', 'u_manager'); //
sys_script_include.name: GlideListToRecords
